Description: Pure C gNMI server for sysrepo
 The smallest, most portable gNMI server for the sysrepo ecosystem.
 A zero-C++ implementation that plugs directly into sysrepo as a
 first-class peer alongside netopeer2 (NETCONF) and Rousette (RESTCONF).
 .
 Features:
  - All 6 gNMI RPCs: Capabilities, Get, Set, Subscribe, Rpc, Confirm
  - Subscribe modes: STREAM (on-change + sample), ONCE, POLL
  - JSON_IETF encoding via libyang C API
  - Single-threaded libevent event loop
  - NACM integration
